                1. Properties: <code>Brand</code> (string), <code>Year</code> (int)<br />
                2. A <strong>constructor</strong> that takes brand and year as parameters<br />
                3. A method <code>DisplayInfo()</code> that prints: "[Brand] made in [Year]"<br />
