        <h2>Exercise 4: Encapsulation</h2>
        <div class="exercise-content">
            <p>
                Create a <strong>BankAccount class</strong> with proper encapsulation:<br />
                1. Private field: <code>balance</code> (decimal)<br />
                2. Public property: <code>Owner</code> (string)<br />
                3. Public methods: <code>Deposit(amount)</code> and <code>GetBalance()</code><br />
                4. Create account for "Alice", deposit 1000, then get balance
            </p>

            <textarea id="code4" rows="10" placeholder="Type your code here..." class="code-input"></textarea>

            <div class="exercise-controls">
                <div class="toggle-container">
                    <label class="switch">
