                1. <strong>Shape class</strong> with <code>virtual</code> method <code>Draw()</code> (prints "Drawing shape")<br />
                2. <strong>Circle class</strong> that inherits from Shape, <code>override</code>s Draw() (prints "Drawing circle")<br />
                3. Create Shape variable that holds Circle object, call Draw()
            </p>

            <textarea id="code5" rows="10" placeholder="Type your code here..." class="code-input"></textarea>

            <div class="exercise-controls">
                <div class="toggle-container">
                    <label class="switch">
