                1. <strong>Game class</strong> with: <code>const MAX_PLAYERS = 4</code>, <code>static playerCount</code>, <code>readonly playerId</code><br />
                2. Constructor sets playerId and increments playerCount<br />
                3. Method to display game info<br />
                4. Create two Game objects and show values
            </p>

            <textarea id="code8" rows="12" placeholder="Type your code here..." class="code-input"></textarea>

            <div class="exercise-controls">
                <div class="toggle-container">
                    <label class="switch">
